# Installation

```bash
composer require pedrotroller/php-cs-custom-fixer --dev
```

### Configuration

```php
// .php_cs.dist
<?php

$config = PhpCsFixer\Config::create()
    // ...
    ->registerCustomFixers(new PedroTroller\CS\Fixer\Fixers())
    // ...
;

return $config;
```

